    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The state of the body of pottery and porcelain after it has partially hardened in consequence of the evaporation of the moisture content.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
